 And then the quarantine is like, yes,

47:11.320 --> 47:13.440
 in that case, if you're quarantining,

47:13.440 --> 47:16.240
 it's because you're shutting the door from the inside,

47:16.240 --> 47:17.080
 if that makes sense.

47:17.080 --> 47:18.120
 Yes, exactly.

47:18.120 --> 47:18.960
 Exactly.

47:18.960 --> 47:20.080
 I mean, this is brilliant.

