 Oh, yeah, I didn't come on here to tell everyone

49:42.040 --> 49:42.880
 to install the app.

49:42.880 --> 49:44.760
 I did not come to tell everyone to install the app

49:44.760 --> 49:46.440
 because it works best

49:46.440 --> 49:49.400
 if your local health authority is working with us.

49:49.400 --> 49:50.240
 Gotcha.

