 There's a reason.

49:51.080 --> 49:53.440
 It's because, this is back to the game theory.

49:54.720 --> 49:57.120
 If anyone could just say, I'm positive,

49:58.320 --> 50:01.840
 the high school senior prank would be to say that

50:01.840 --> 50:03.960
 we have a massive outbreak on finals week.

50:03.960 --> 50:05.240
 Let's not have final exams.

