 I think that being able to look at a complicated problem,

52:26.880 --> 52:28.560
 which looks unsolvable,

52:28.560 --> 52:30.800
 and then to be able to change the perspective

52:30.800 --> 52:32.480
 to come from a different angle

52:32.480 --> 52:36.160
 and suddenly see that there's a nice solution.

